Author: xenomorphe1
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: What will happen if someone working at the City of EDEN got fired? Or if he retired? Can he still live in the City of EDEN? And how does he get paid for his work?

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: The City of EDEN and all of our products and services are traditional revenue model based companies that are for profit with the one change that we focus on top level life changing solutions that work towards solving the world's problems.  Employees that are also residents get free housing, food and competitive salaries. Just like with a traditional corporation if someone is being laid off they will have a period to make arrangements.  If they are being fired as in they did something illegal, dangerous or harmful to the company then they would be asked to leave relatively quickly.  That being said it's the reason why we have invested so many resources into the EDEN Distributed Network. It is our method of recruiting the best talent. Before ever being invited to live in the City of EDEN we invite people to come on temporary stays and on trial runs.  Living and working together are all very different things. So making sure that the entire team and environment is compatible with the potential recruit and vice versa is extremely important to us.  Though we are only 1 hour from Bogota a major and really fun city not everyone wants to be living in nature. To that end we are also in the process of partnering with co-working facilities around the world to provide token holders free entry to remote labs and offices closer to where they live.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: Thanks... We agree! EDEN stands for Engineering Design & Entrepreneurship in Nature. Originally we thought of Beta for the name of our company and city because it represented we were never done with our exploration, testing and creation.  After sleeping on it Beta didn't seem right so we brain stormed again.  I Googled "synonyms for paradise" and Eden was one of the synonyms. At first I didn't really like the name so much but when we came up with the acronym it felt really perfect.  If you want to dive deeper we wrote an article on it - http://blog.cityofeden.io/why-we-built-eden/

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: Thank you! That was very meaningful to me and the team. I honestly don't think we are the first to think up these concepts but we're just doing it. We risked our own money and avoided doing a token sale until we actually built something.  You can review our smart contract and token on Github - https://github.com/cityofeden/EDEN-smart-contracts  Here's a quick overview: Add open source solutions to posted technical and creative bounties on projects in Blockchain, Aerospace, Med & Bio Tech and Renewables. Technical contributions are published as open source and remain open and available for others to use at no cost. Verified contributions will be rewarded with EDN Tokens. Submit new projects and build teams around them to collaborate and execute on projects. As you achieve more within your project you and your team level up and earn more EDN tokens. Gain access to perform peer review on the blockchain. Validate contributions in the EDEN Distributed Network and get rewarded in EDN tokens. Higher level EDN token holders gain higher levels of access and invitations to exclusive events, trips and short term stays to the City of EDEN and eventually permanent residency where you earn competitive salaries, live for free with top amenities and services and work on high level projects with access to bleeding edge research and development facilities. EDN Tokens can be used to purchase products and services from EDEN Companies. See all EDEN companies, products and services here.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: We have not announced the price of Heavy Neon yet. It's an industrial drone and we are pricing it significantly less than our competitor (there's really only one in this weight class currently.  Only token holders can pre-order. It's one of the benefits of being a token holder. You will be able to purchase using traditional methods in the future.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: Currently it is Motorola... We're working on some pretty special things with them that we will announce a little later.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: You can read more about the utility here: https://github.com/cityofeden/EDEN-smart-contracts  The TL;DR version is that you earn more tokens with more contributions. Different bounties and challenges yield different EDN rewards and different levels and badges amplify your earning potential.  So earning EDN tokens and gaining access to abilities like publishing your own bounties within your own projects with your own assembled team are both project specific and individual specific.  The concept is to remove the barrier completely for a potential solution to emerge.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: Yes but we made it extremely easy for someone to become a token holder. With more tokens you unlock more abilities and earning potential but to get started you just need an email and a will to solve problems.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: Learn more about The City of EDEN and the EDN token below Join us on Telegram to ask us any questions you have  TL;DR: We bought the top of a mountain to build a city of engineers. The plan is to bring great thinkers and doers together in order to solve the world's greatest challenges. We involve the global community of problems solvers through the EDEN Distributed Network in which people contribute open source solutions to challenges that we publish. Contributors are rewarded through EDN tokens which can be used for free education, engineering and design equipment, trips and residence to The City of EDEN and the end products and services.  What we've accomplished: This is more than a nice idea. 9 of us are living the pilot in a rented a property where we have built 3 solutions in IoT, industrial drones and med tech. In addition we've secured key distribution partners to our tech and have purchased the land in which The City of EDEN will be built on.  WEBSITE | WHITEPAPER | BOUNTY PROGRAM  | TWITTER | FACEBOOK | TELEGRAM | REDDIT | BLOG | GITHUB   https://i.imgur.com/dRH80EM.jpg

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: We are a group of engineers that have already built 3 life changing solutions (hardware + software). We purchased a plot of land at the top of a mountain where we are building a city of engineers that live and work together to solve the worlds problems.  We then leverage our distributed community of problem solvers to contribute open source solutions to the projects we are working on and they get rewarded in EDN tokens. These contributions are how we validate people's problem solving abilities and ultimately is our approach to hiring.  Residents of The City of EDEN earn competitive salaries and live and eat for free.

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: We use blockchain in several ways and blockchain is a foundation of our product development.  1) All contributor attribution is run through the blockchain (it means no one else can every claim they created something you did). 2) Peer review on the blockchain (it means we are reducing the fraud and corruption that currently exists in the scientific and medical peer review community. Read this article: https://newrepublic.com/article/135921/science-suffering-peer-reviews-big-problems). 3) All of our products current and future are built with the blockchain. These products include an IoT hardware and software solution, and industrial drone that can lift 270kg and a surgical tool loss prevention hardware and software. Each and every product in EDEN leverages the foundation of the blockchain which is security, trust and transparency. 4) All contracts and agreements in The City of EDEN are smart contracts.  If you have a moment please read our whitepaper: https://view.attach.io/BkJ6BulwG

Author: barney_stinson
Title: [ANN][TOKEN] City of EDEN (EDN Token)
Body: We are a United States based company with The City of EDEN our base of R&D in Colombia and we have satellite offices in Israel and Ukraine.
